        <h2 style={{ fontFamily: "'Syne', sans-serif", fontWeight: 800, fontSize: "clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem)", color: COLORS.walnut, textAlign: "center", margin: "0 0 4rem", letterSpacing: "-0.02em" }}>Tre Pilastri di Eccellenza</h2>
